  "title": "feat(refinementList): merge showMore templates",
  "body": "This implements #3318 for the `refinementList` widget.\r\n\r\nIt also fixes an error thrown where no templates are given but the `showMore` option is used, by giving a default `showMoreText` template (like for `hierarchicalMenu` and `menu`).\r\n\r\n## Stories\r\n\r\nhttps://deploy-preview-3329--instantsearchjs.netlify.com/stories/?selectedStory=RefinementList.with%20show%20more%20and%20templates",
